  "body": "# ðŸ’Ž Issue\r\nWe have done some work to clean up the beacon node initialization process using [functional options](https://dave.cheney.net/2014/10/17/functional-options-for-friendly-apis). The validator cli hasn't had this makeover yet, which would be an improvement for the addition of more cli flags, like the fee recipient config.\r\n\r\n### Background\r\n\r\nexamples of functional options being generated from flags (which are also pushed into the component-specific flag handling package):\r\n  - https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/develop/cmd/beacon-chain/blockchain/options.go\r\n  - https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/develop/cmd/beacon-chain/powchain/options.go\r\n\r\nhow the FlagOptions are set up and passed in to the beacon-chain node: https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/develop/cmd/beacon-chain/main.go#L234-L246\r\nvariadic argument on node.New: https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/develop/beacon-chain/node/node.go#L108\r\napplying the opts: https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/develop/beacon-chain/node/node.go#L149\r\nopt definitions: https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/develop/beacon-chain/node/options.go\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nUpdate the validator cli to use the same functional options pattern as beacon-chain.",
